NK017(tsa)001:0: man ngag rdzong 'phrang srog gsum gyi bla brgyud gsol bdebs bzhugs so //
NK017(tsa)001:1: ston pa kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK017(tsa)001:2: rab dgyes rdo rje dpal ldan seng ge 'od //
NK017(tsa)001:3: mkhas pa mi bzhi zhing drung ye shes gzhon //
NK017(tsa)001:4: gnubs chen yab sras rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK017(tsa)001:5: pad+ma dbang rgyal tshul khrims rgyal mtshan dang //
NK017(tsa)001:6: ldan brtson ye shes dbang phyug se ston pa //
NK017(tsa)001:7: dngos grub nyang ral 'gro mgon chos dbang zhabs //
NK017(tsa)001:8: pad+ma dbang chen rnams la shes rab rgya mtsho zur ham sh+aakya 'byung //
NK017(tsa)001:9: sh+aaka rdor bshes dpal gnyis dang ra legs zung //
NK017(tsa)001:10: rin rgyal mnga' ris pan chen ngag gi dbang //
NK017(tsa)001:11: tshe brtan rgyal po rnams la nam mkhar spyod pa pa ra hi ta dang //
NK017(tsa)001:12: phrin las lhun grub 'gyur med rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK017(tsa)001:13: rin chen rnam rgyal o rgyan rig 'dzin dang //
NK017(tsa)001:14: theg mchog brtan 'dzin rnams la bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan rig 'dzin rgya mtsho dang //
NK017(tsa)001:15: phrin las dar rgyas pad+ma bkra shis dpal //
NK017(tsa)001:16: pad+ma rdo rje kun bzang chos kyi grags //
NK017(tsa)001:17: khyab bdag phan bde'i 'od zer la gsol ba 'debs //
NK017(tsa)001:18: mkhyen brtse'i mnga' bdag rtsa brgyud bla ma la //
NK017(tsa)001:19: bzod med gdung shugs drag pos gsol 'debs na //
NK017(tsa)001:20: tshad med thugs rje chen pos nyer dgongs te //
NK017(tsa)001:21: bdag rgyud byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol //
NK017(tsa)001:22: tshe 'di'i mngon zhen ldog par byin gyis rlobs //
NK017(tsa)001:23: bden bzhi'i 'jug ldog shes par byin byang chub sems
NK017(tsa)001:24: gnyis 'byong par byin smin grol lam la 'jug par
NK017(tsa)001:25: byin bskyed rdzogs zab gnad rtogs par byin bsnyen sgrub
NK017(tsa)001:26: mtha' ru phyin par byin sku bzhi'i rgyal srid zin
NK017(tsa)001:27: par byin rang gzhan don gnyis 'grub par byin gyis
NK017(tsa)001:28: rlobs // zhes rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas kyi
NK017(tsa)001:29: gsung la brgyud pa'i khyad par gyis gter chen nas
NK017(tsa)001:30: rang gi bla ma'i bar brgyud rim kha skong ba
